flan.command.help.1: Shows all available commands or info for the given command.
flan.command.menu.1: When standing in a claim you have permissions for opens the claim menu.
flan.command.claimInfo.1: Prints infos about the claim you're standing in.
flan.command.deleteAll.1: Deletes all your claims (you need to double type to confirm it so no accidents).
flan.command.deleteAllSubClaims.1: Deletes all subclaim of the current claim.
flan.command.list.1: Lists all claims you have. If op also gives ability to list other players claims.
flan.command.switchMode.1: Switch between normal and subclaim mode.
flan.command.group.1: - Adds/removes the group with that name. Also editable via the claim menu.
flan.command.group.2: - Adds/remove a player to the group. If overwrite then will overwrite the players current group else does nothing. Also editable via the claim menu.
flan.command.transferClaim.1: Gives ownership of the claim to the specified player. Only works if you're the claim owner.
flan.command.addClaim.0: addClaim (<x y z> <x y z>) | all | (rect x z)
flan.command.addClaim.1: Creates a claim with the given positions. Same as using the claim tool.
flan.command.addClaim.2: <all> uses up all remaining blocks for a squared claim centered around the player
flan.command.addClaim.3: <rect> creates a rectangular claim centered around the player
flan.command.permission.1: Sets global/group/personal permissions. Also editable via the claim menu (for group perm right click on the group in the menu).
flan.command.personalGroups.1: Opens the gui to edit personal groups.
flan.command.sellBlocks.1: Sells <amount> claimblocks. Needs gunpowder currency installed.
flan.command.buyBlocks.1: Buys <amount> claimblocks. Needs gunpowder currency installed.
flan.command.trapped.1: If in a claim not owned by the player attempts to teleport the player out of it after 5 seconds.
flan.command.unlockDrops.1: Unlocks dropped items from death so other players can pick them up too. Or all of the given players (needs OP)
flan.command.setHome.1: Standing in a claim with sufficient permission sets that claims home to the players position
flan.command.teleport.1: Teleport to the given claims home position. Use admin to teleport to admin claims
flan.command.claimMessage.1: Sets the claims message. Use "$empty" to remove the message
flan.command.ignoreList.1: Adds/Removes an entry to the claim specific ignore list
flan.command.adminMode.1: Switches to admin mode ignoring all claims.
flan.command.readGriefPrevention.1: Parses data from the GriefPrevention plugin to Flan
flan.command.setAdminClaim.1: Sets a claim to an admin claim.
flan.command.listAdminClaims.1: Lists all admin claims in the current world.
flan.command.adminDelete.1: Force deletes the current claim or deletes all claims from the specified player.
flan.command.giveClaimBlocks.1: Gives a player additional claim blocks.
